ring）：为期2年*(3)(4)(7)</li>	<li>计算核科学与工程博士（Joint PhD in Computational Nuclear Science &amp; Engineering）：为期4-7年（视论文完成情况）*(3)(5)(7)</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/核工程师" target="_blank">核工程师</a>（Nuclear Engineer）：为期2年*(3)(6)(7)</li></ul><p>注：核工程专业为签证高度敏感专业。</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>核科学与工程系有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>裂变（Fission）</li>	<li>核聚变（Fusion）</li>	<li>核安全（Nuclear Security）</li>	<li>辐射源、探测与测量（Radiation Sources, Detection &amp; Measurement）</li>	<li>建模与模拟（Modeling &amp; Simulation）</li>	<li>极端环境下材料（Materials in Extreme Environments）*(8)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;教员列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aGb5khMQaWuF1111110rEay1z_AkcRbzLI6y3VbOV51GHgum3Itnx7-DSQsk3VKuTSP-5BKulQN1Z5qe" target="_blank">Faculty</a></p><p>&middot;&nbsp;常见问题：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Gr-dDk55LjdAsoogwwwwwwCkz9yf1ohR0xnrmLoaDaHtxaM_YJojrK1eoJ9ohYJ-zgJYS92IYGmzLzh5" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a></p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://registrar.mit.edu/registration-academics/tuition-fees" target="_blank">Graduate Thesis Tuition Rules</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="https://registrar.mit.edu/sites/default/files/2019-04/tuition_19-20.pdf" target="_blank">Graduate Thesis Tuition Rules 2019-2020</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTdwLMS38_FkSSSSSSE9dVsJ-igqVeUXFEWJP1KAY9xoVyrY4AI5dA7qnOUi9foRtAmK31h2vThxHLkWaLYbto6FTIYJ5" target="_blank">Graduate Admissions</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7P7kjzL8vQheeeeee0N1ZvQ8naSyr4VX35N6f0gDZkSK37gRH4g1IcV6ZlqKLagyPOghXTSXFs52U8AolN" target="_blank">GRADUATE : Doctoral Degree Requirements</a>&nbsp;NSE Department, MIT</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=vrJH6YymwnkBwXZyJJJJJJ-nE8gbptx9Pdm3oSKuE7-klngjPcKFl5z3l80qo7gYWcI9ldDNlGzupXKxmLjNM" target="_blank">GRADUATE : Mast