target="_blank">机械工程</a>（<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/机械工程" target="_blank">Mechanical Engineering</a>）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/核工程" target="_blank">核科学与工程</a>（Nuclear Science and Engineering）*(9)</li></ul><p>计算工程中心有从应用层面讲，有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>材料与制造（A1: Materials &amp; Manufacturing）</li>	<li>微纳米系统（A2: Nano/Micro Systems）</li>	<li>生物与<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/生物医学" target="_blank">生物医学</a>过程/系统（A3: Biological &amp; Biomedical Processes/Systems）</li>	<li>基础设施系统与服务（A4: Infrastructure Systems &amp; Services）</li>	<li>能源（A5: Energy）</li>	<li>环境（A6: Environment）</li>	<li>交通（A7: Transportation）*(11)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="https://registrar.mit.edu/registration-academics/tuition-fees" target="_blank">Graduate Thesis Tuition Rules</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="https://registrar.mit.edu/sites/default/files/2019-04/tuition_19-20.pdf" target="_blank">Graduate Thesis Tuition Rules 2019-2020</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aG4FL6UOjg3R11111FNnuah5mwnorvm0dOcYQlEfNeKqXrk4KaHB8wZrjodtfBPt4pv8Lpe0Lxy1uGz1-JThE-baZJkWSpFXCcAN8skCL3M0d5lXCZFewNVGL" target="_blank">Graduate Admissions</a><a href="https://cce.mit.edu/admissions/cse/" target="_blank">&nbsp;Deadline&nbsp;</a>Center for Computational Engineering, MIT</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nH7xLyQ825UZ2HINfN-_bAWiuiCqVP168DOgtygHcoSBAS-se00zWDqZzoEAmg7rAmkB6kfCrwyN1VNnChTzEnizqkwbY4GGLElaw3EBbZ" target="_blank">Information for CDO Applicants</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyf9Ln0yNcAUHHHHHH9N1MDVaz9pCt924KIE6mDN3e-bGMA3Nnm09dUYjQUjxzR7yF6HQuZWdomEeGC9eJnUbz" target="_blank">CDO Frequently Asked Questions</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aG4fL_HK0X89VVVVVVm7BOm2ytISvlIsQUK3rMm7k0L8kZhsj