k">机械工程</a>系、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/电气工程" target="_blank">电气工程与计算机科学</a>系、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/土木工程" target="_blank">土木与环境工程</a>系。*(1)</p><p>该项目不同专业方向，对申请者专业背景及前置课程要求稍有不同，专业背景要求见下，前置课程列表请见外部链接：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:26.66%">			<p>专业方向</p>			</td>			<td style="width:73.34%">			<p>专业背景要求</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:26.66%">			<p>应用<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/海洋科学" target="_blank">海洋科学</a>与工程</p>			</td>			<td style="width:73.34%">			<p>工程、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/物理" target="_blank">物理</a>科学</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:26.66%">			<p>生物海洋地理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:73.34%">			<p>生物学基础学科</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:26.66%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/化学" target="_blank">化学</a>海洋地理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:73.34%">			<p>物理科学，并具备强大的化学基础</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:26.66%">			<p>海洋地理与<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/地球物理" target="_blank">地球物理</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:73.34%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/地质学" target="_blank">地质学</a>、物理、化学、地球物理、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/地球科学" target="_blank">地球科学</a>、数学、工程</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:26.66%">			<p>物理海洋地理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:73.34%">			<p>工程、物理科学、数学、气象学</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(6)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>伍兹霍尔海洋研究所有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>气候与海洋（Climate &amp; Ocean）</li>	<li>海岸科学（Coastal Science）</li>	<li>海洋灾害（Hazards）</li>	<li>海洋化学（Ocean <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/化学" target="_blank">Chemistry</a>）</li>	<li>海洋环流（Ocean Circulation）</li>	<li>海洋生命（Ocean Life）</li>	<li>海洋资源与政策（Ocean Resources &amp; Policy）</li>	<li>极性系统（Polar Systems）</li>	<li>海洋污染（Pollution）</li>	<li>海底（Seafloor &amp; Below）</li>	<li>海洋探测工具与技术（Tools &amp; Technology）</li>	<li>水下<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/考古学" target="_blank">考古学</a>（Underwater Archaeology）*(8)</li></ul><p>MIT-WHOI联合项目有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>应用海洋科学与工程（Applied Ocean Science and Engineering）</li>	<li>生物海洋学（Biological Oceanography）</li>	<li>化学海洋学（Chemical Oceanography）</li>	<li>海洋地理与地球物理（Marine Geology and Geophysics）</li>	<li>物理海洋学（Physical Oceanography）</li>	<li>交叉研究（Interdisciplinary Focus）	<ul>		<li>应用海洋科学与工程（Applied Ocean Science &amp; Engineering）</li>		<li>生物海洋学（Biological Oceanography）</li>		<li>化学海洋学（Chemical Oceanography）</li>		<li>海洋地理与地球物理（Marine Geology &amp; Geophysics）</li>		<li>物理海洋学（Physical Oceanography）</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>气候多变性及其影响（Climate Variability and Impacts）*(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;前置课程列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzNWw_8kIm0OKKKKKKIm6CpP_xAM1bRTJcVQ2dfa2IEwPQ_WFMyPnc0EUJgw6pb" target="_blank">Undergraduate Preparation</a></p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2usLWal5BPTaaaaa13hDAUIk0fs6bHLS2tWDxvL6Fc4SgvTk3IF9fax" target="_blank">Applying</a>&nbsp;MIT/WHOI Joint Program</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJR6RwySz7EqHoooooo5VZWuwBGQgxSVUbGAMCCMwsCvh4nPY-5k_pD8HSrwO-_yJbT0L" target="_blank">How to Apply</a>&nbsp;MIT/WHOI Joint Program</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=VrxbIdt6LFLdYMEeBBBBBBszkwSXx4APpADjHBaSUfVMWTqbLGS1HNh92T-" target="_blank">Admission FAQs</a>&nbsp;MIT/WHOI Joint Program</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=urKrNASVkPIupgpxrrrrrrcLXhlvPj48w6WywoW8g6fHxUWOXI4yJSoOdb_LJe4O-RoOXboF2X9P" target="_blank">Graduate Programs</a>&nbsp;ME Department, MIT</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caJvwlsJdP-dGGGGGGxweEp678N_sAfDdOJwmQf_tc3DPQh6tQx6tJbvgsWQOP2xYBMKYsV9" target="_blank">Program Description</a>&nbsp;MIT/WHOI Joint Program</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZi9Ln0yNcWMIIIIIIs50qNKtiOYRDbsM-15pfbYlFBs8fjpP839r85six_" target="_blank">Undergraduate Preparation</a>&nbsp;MIT/WHOI Joint Program</p><p>(7)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=srULj0-SwHR2VfSYWWWWWWyqLySZFUJ4efwV9qsojSioOZx8DpGxEUsxT64nE7QbEnQF" target="_blank">Admissions Statistics</a>&nbsp;MIT/WHOI Joint Program</p><p>(8)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=PrgaXqIjk78ysqr-ppppppcH2fVzi5M7Y9amamNva5ARxbr6LTGNsLOjV_6P0ePENTPGP0TyW0MQBKbQJKbEHY" target="_blank">Areas of Research</a>&nbsp;Woods Hole Oceanographic Institution</p><p>(9)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhMKkgdlWuTozzzzzzSS6O4amcLCYtW1o-sSrXWCFq51hXFSPqeB6i" target="_blank">Fields of Study</a>&nbsp;MIT:WHOL Joint Program in Oceanography/Applied Ocean Science &amp; Engineering</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>其他项目</h3><p>麻省理工学院高分子与软物质项目（Program in Polymers and Soft Matter，缩写：PPSM）属交叉学科项目，由工程学院与理学院共同开设，授予PhD学位。该项目面向以下科系研究生招生：</p><ul>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/生物工程" target="_blank">生物工程</a></li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/化学工程" target="_blank">化学工程</a></li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/化学" target="_blank">化学</a></li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/材料科学与工程" target="_blank">材料科学与工程</a></li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/机械工程" target="_blank">机械工程</a>*(1)(2)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;高分子与软物质项目教员列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTdALEo5iAcKssssss478r4diE2LTOlru_Gs2ubI9dm744A2ytxpyIQ_fZVbv5ripYUfX4DOGzkNqndsz" target="_blank">Faculty</a></p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=JrvWrUjjL5VUFGluhhhhhhbiXtru7-W_GItzvVt3vWSHFx5H-3Z9gxeD_bEsiV91bVX1fOwterl8J6fqzQa0" target="_blank">PROGRAM IN POLYMERS AND SOFT MATTER</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwaskL3ojClmddddddQ4iCp0JFlDUnlsifKh7S13EffsZLfDZXQ9m_fhiVlRUnxhEya4NveA1gX" target="_blank">PPSM Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>建筑与规划学院</h2><h3>建筑学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.8%">			<p><a href="htt