<p>(1) <a href="https://registrar.mit.edu/registration-academics/tuition-fees" target="_blank">Graduate Thesis Tuition Rules</a> Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(2) <a href="https://registrar.mit.edu/sites/default/files/2019-04/tuition_19-20.pdf" target="_blank">Graduate Thesis Tuition Rules 2019-2020</a> Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIezt2eLPImadPeJot8hDt9lnaX0LWt7xbwp5Hrwjz386Ay-wcaEUj0satS_cmS1Cs-pMCrsF2zhUcmM84m9hqrPdyqTYrFbglDXZIhUrhaMGH4tsyXVPlJyaL6ofjOUqtP0" target="_blank">Graduate Admissions</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=PrgaXqI6kBHWJpEtOOOOOOqrjEEqGXUd1l85Gjk7PYXhoL1xCSOcryEBtpdIay0x38d96RdxusZUgYZxtLJ8t-mgNR9ycROLF" target="_blank">Research Areas in EAPS</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>健康科学与技术项目</h2><p>哈佛-麻省理工<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/健康科学" target="_blank">健康科学</a>技术项目（Harvard-MIT Program in Health Sciences and Technology，缩写：HST）联合麻省理工学院、哈佛<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/医学" target="_blank">医学</a>院、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/哈佛大学" target="_blank">哈佛大学</a>以及<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/波士顿" target="_blank">波士顿</a>地区众多教学医院共同开设有以下学位项目，分别是：*(1)</p><ul>	<li>医学博士（Doctor of Medicine，缩写：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/MD" target="_blank">MD</a>）：为期4-5年，由哈佛医学院主导，要求国际学生本科毕业，必须在美国或加拿大修完大部分前置课程，因此国内本科毕业的学生无法直接申请此项目*(2)(3)</li>	<li>医学工程与医学物理博士（PhD in Medical Engineering and Medical <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/物理" target="_blank">Physics</a>，缩写：MEMP）：为期5-7年，由麻省理工学院和哈佛<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/文理学院" target="_blank">文理学院</a>共同开设，要求申请者本科毕业，拥有工程或物理科学专业背景，需递交GRE考试成绩，但未设定最低分数要求，被录取的学生通常GRE阅读<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/百分比排名" target="_blank">百分比排名</a>75%以上，GRE<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/数学" target="_blank">数学</a>和写作百分比排名90%以上，需递交TOEFL/IELTS考试成绩，分别不低于100分和7.0分。所有被录取的生均可获得全额<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>，第一年主要以Fellowship）奖学金，第二年即以<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TA" target="_blank">TA</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a>的形式授予奖学金，含学费、医疗保险和生活补助。该项目可通过麻省理工学院或哈佛文理学院申请，截止日期分别为12月15日和12月1日*(4)(5)(6)</li>	<li>言语与听觉生物科学技术（Speech and Hearing Bioscience and Technology，缩写：SHBT）：已于2012年移入哈佛医学院医学科学部*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;教员列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5cOwp7HoglJNyK2umzEZPu02y5h6PWoKrz6Ogf8PjvgQh6bcd9t4gfY1jbq-WO1xRpEVcm8hOPWj" target="_blank">HST Faculty</a></p><p>&middot;&nbsp;课程列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2QqweEscMGn------Wm6CpP_xAMGwtOsxny0hzgvmDh75r89AWRliqKDtUhyiLhKDsgiyEgP" target="_blank">Courses</a></p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRvJkIT16iwcKFFogs_Ox662tNW3ZYAbfzlP3Osrnz2qbUUuW-chuVPH_35z9iK" target="_blank">About HST</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibvEwgqXD45pbbbbbbFARjDXMlLoymOfpTeA542Uujhoy1NZujstusNXSPeUb" target="_blank">MD Program</a>&nbsp;HST, Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUw06LFLdYTWMIIIIIIf50qNKtiOYRguKx-iCcARCcABYlFyixlQimzJFPqriQAFYGjg53A8l9jmp9foY4ehd2LSuMDpdM3S5vmoC2jp7" target="_blank">MD Admissions FAQs</a>&nbsp;Harvard Medical School</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7PwkxAv4jvZ999999gWzmQpSBfJtgXeZYwWklcxLm7JtnTULmaGLaTpIrwxL7_" target="_blank">Medical Engineering and Medical Physics (MEMP)</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=grPZ_xIsLWal5BSfFFFFFFDGmzlRxua8OJ-ahp0IHtxaM_YJ7Lk2G_YK6_K2uVd1NhJH56bK4YJ7okb7sYPR" target="_blank">MEMP Admissions</a>&nbsp;Massachusetts Institute of Technology</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKN2L4yTxHNjZRu10u-J7pf3Jf0SALP2a0eThBbjdTJbM-2RPHhPGnhBbVLxxPOtYP4brScWrH6z5x74ZwJe7Oa695SG7nkbFVk" target="_blank">FAQ for Prospective MEMP students</a>&nb